<title>yạrb lyk ạlḥmd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yạ rb lyk ạlḥmd wạlqwẗ wạlslṭạn

[V2]
 rfʿt lyk ạlmjd yạ syd ạlạ̉kwạn

[V3]
 jbạl ạ̉ssthạ wdyạn mhdthạ

[V4]
 wṣnʿt mnạ ạ̹lhy nfws lyk ḥmdhạ

[V5]
 yạ kẖạlq kl sẖyʾ bḥkmẗ wạqtdạr

[V6]
 tsbyḥy yʿlạ lyk wqlby lyk ạ̉wtạr

[V7]
 klạmy mạ ykfysẖ ạ̉lḥạny mạtwfysẖ

[V8]
 lkn yạ rb mạlysẖ gẖyr ạ̹ny ạ̉sbḥk</lyrics>
</song>